OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPensions to get boost as   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftax-free limit to rise     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The total amount that workers can      
OL,6, accumulate in their pension savings    
OL,7, before paying extra tax is expected to 
OL,8, be increased in Wednesday's Budget.    
OL,10,FThe final figure has not been          
OL,11,Fconfirmed, but people are expected to  
OL,12,Fbe able to save up to #1.8m over a     
OL,13,Flifetime, up from #1.07m currently.    
OL,15,FThe policy aims to stop people -       
OL,16,Fparticularly doctors - from reducing   
OL,17,Fhours or retiring early owing to tax.  
OL,19,FCritics say the move will only benefit 
OL,20,Fa small fraction of the workforce.     
